name: Familiar-Possessed - Wynn
text: You can send 1 "Wynn the Wind Charmer" and 1 WIND monster you control to the Graveyard to Special Summon this card from your hand or Deck. If you do, this card gets the following effect: ? During battle between this attacking card and a Defense Position monster whose DEF is lower than the ATK of this card, inflict the difference as Battle Damage to your opponent.
